---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import step1 from "../../assets/images/step-01.png";
import step2 from "../../assets/images/step-02.png";
import step3 from "../../assets/images/step-03.png";
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-[#f4faff]">
  <div class="w-[90%] lg:w-[75%] max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
    {/* Headings Collection */}
    <div class="mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <h3
        class="text-[#00BFA5] font-bold tracking-wider text-sm md:text-base uppercase mb-3"
      >
        Tu Primer Turno
      </h3>
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6 font-['Poppins',sans-serif]"
      >
        Reserva tu turno en <span class="text-[#00BFA5]">3 Simples Pasos.</span>
      </h2>

      <p class="text-slate-800 font-semibold text-lg md:text-xl mb-4">
        Para poder acceder a la Agenda Virtual:
      </p>

      <ul
        class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-700 font-medium space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg ml-2"
      >
        <li>
          Hacer click en el boton <span class="text-[#00BFA5] font-bold"
            >"Pedir Turno"</span
          > o <span class="text-[#00BFA5] font-bold">"Reservar Turno"</span> dentro
          de este sitio.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    {/* Steps Container */}
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-16 md:gap-24 w-full">
      {/* --- STEP 1 --- */}
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8 lg:gap-12 w-full"
      >
        {/* Texts */}
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-start xl:pl-10">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-start gap-6 w-full">
            <div
              class="bg-[#dcf4ef] text-[#00BFA5] text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold px-5 py-3 md:px-8 md:py-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm leading-none shrink-0"
            >
              1
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col mt-2 md:mt-4">
              <h3
                class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 font-['Poppins',sans-serif] mb-6"
              >
                Elegi tu servicio
              </h3>
              <ul
                class="space-y-6 text-slate-700 font-medium text-base md:text-lg"
              >
                <li class="relative pl-6">
                  <span
                    class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"
                  ></span>
                  <span class="font-bold italic"
                    >Estando ya en la agenda virtual, podras visualizar todos
                    los servicios (Kinesiologia, Estetica/salud, Otros)</span
                  >
                </li>
                <li class="relative pl-6">
                  <span
                    class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"
                  ></span>
                  Una vez decidido el servicio clickear en el boton <span
                    class="text-[#00BFA5] font-bold">"Agendar servicio"</span
                  >
                </li>
                <li class="relative pl-6">
                  <span
                    class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"
                  ></span>
                  Luego en la parte inferior de la pantalla clickear el boton <span
                    class="text-[#00BFA5] font-bold">"Agendar ahora"</span
                  > para continuar.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Image */}
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
          <Image
            src={step1}
            alt="Paso 1: Agenda virtual con lista de servicios"
            class="w-full h-auto object-contain"
            width={800}
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* --- STEP 2 --- */}
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-8 lg:gap-12 w-full"
      >
        {/* Texts */}
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-start xl:pl-10">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-start gap-6 w-full">
            <div
              class="bg-[#dcf4ef] text-[#00BFA5] text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold px-5 py-3 md:px-8 md:py-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm leading-none shrink-0"
            >
              2
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col mt-2 md:mt-4">
              <h3
                class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 font-['Poppins',sans-serif] mb-6"
              >
                Seleccioná fecha y horario
              </h3>
              <ul
                class="space-y-6 text-slate-700 font-medium text-base md:text-lg"
              >
                <li class="relative pl-6">
                  <span
                    class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"
                  ></span>
                  <span class="font-bold italic"
                    >En la nueva pantalla podras visualizar un calendario y la
                    informacion del servicio que seleccionaste</span
                  >
                </li>
                <li class="relative pl-6">
                  <span
                    class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"
                  ></span>
                  Seleccionar fecha y horario que te quede mas comodo.
                </li>
                <li class="relative pl-6">
                  <span
                    class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"
                  ></span>
                  Luego clickear el boton <span class="text-[#00BFA5] font-bold"
                    >"Agendar ahora"</span
                  >
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Image */}
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
          <Image
            src={step2}
            alt="Paso 2: Selección de fecha y horario"
            class="w-full h-auto object-contain"
            width={800}
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* --- STEP 3 --- */}
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8 lg:gap-12 w-full"
      >
        {/* Texts */}
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-start xl:pl-10">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-start gap-6 w-full">
            <div
              class="bg-[#dcf4ef] text-[#00BFA5] text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold px-5 py-3 md:px-8 md:py-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm leading-none shrink-0"
            >
              3
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col mt-2 md:mt-4">
              <h3
                class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 font-['Poppins',sans-serif] mb-6"
              >
                Completa tus datos
              </h3>
              <ul
                class="space-y-6 text-slate-700 font-medium text-base md:text-lg"
              >
                <li class="relative pl-6">
                  <span
                    class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"
                  ></span>
                  <span class="font-bold italic"
                    >En la nueva pantalla podras visualizar un formulario y la
                    informacion del servicio actualizada.</span
                  >
                </li>
                <li class="relative pl-6">
                  <span
                    class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"
                  ></span>
                  Rellenar formulario con tus datos de contacto.
                </li>
                <li class="relative pl-6">
                  <span
                    class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"
                  ></span>
                  Clickear el boton <span class="text-[#00BFA5] font-bold"
                    >"Agendar"</span
                  > para finalizar
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Image */}
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
          <Image
            src={step3}
            alt="Paso 3: Formulario de datos"
            class="w-full h-auto object-contain"
            width={800}
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
